159
00:08:30.600 --> 00:08:32.011
Wat zeg je daarop?

160
00:08:35.720 --> 00:08:38.644
Ik zeg daarop...

161
00:08:39.840 --> 00:08:40.841
Welkom.

162
00:08:41.320 --> 00:08:42.162
Welkom.

163
00:08:42.320 --> 00:08:43.321
Driewerf...

164
00:08:43.480 --> 00:08:44.481
welkom...

165
00:08:44.680 --> 00:08:46.250
